item.description:
send alert Use Webhook, Create Channel and Webhook in Mattermost, and put script to $(grep AlertScriptsPath /etc/zabbix/zabbix_server.conf). Create Media types in Zabbix(Administration -&gt; Medai types). Add media to user(Administration -&gt; Users -&gt; Media). Create action(Configuration -&gt; Actions -&gt; Trigger actions)。 Debug(Write log in script). Media types: PROBLEM:
Problem started at {EVENT.TIME} on {EVENT.DATE}
 問題: {EVENT.NAME}
 主機: {HOST.NAME}
Severity: {EVENT.SEVERITY}
 目前數值: {EVENT.OPDATA}
 問題 ID: {EVENT.ID}
{TRIGGER.URL} RECOVERY:
Problem has been resolved at {EVENT.RECOVERY.TIME} on {EVENT.
